The '''See Change Festival''' is a biennial [[arts festival]] held in the [[Jervis Bay]] and [[St Georges Basin (New South Wales)|St Georges Basin]] area, of the [[City of Shoalhaven]], in late May and early June. The festival was first held in 2000. Festival events are themed around visual and performing arts, and literature, including photography, film, painting, sculpture, story writing, poetry and music. See Change is the sister festival of [[See Celebrations]].

